{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"906f845e2f","title":"关于支持情报局刊物对野坂参三的批评致胡乔木电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d90ee9e12f","index":0,"year":1950,"month":1,"day":14,"articleId":"906f845e2f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"287ee171b2","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"906f845e2f","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"野圾参三，即冈野进，当时任日本共产党中央政治局委员。胡乔木，当时任中央人民政府新闻总署署长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"776b944d1b","type":"title","text":"关于支持情报局刊物对野坂参三的批评致胡乔术叫电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"906f845e2f"},{"id":"287ee171b2","type":"paragraph","text":"乔木同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"906f845e2f"},{"id":"e19584a891","type":"paragraph","text":"我今晚九时动身去列宁城参观，要三天才能回来，而人民日报社论稿及日共政治局的决议尚未收到。如要等我看过，须到十七日才有复电，否则由少奇同志看过即可发表。我党应当发表意见，支持情报局刊物对冈野进的批评，而对于日共政治局未能接受此批评表示烧惜，希望日共采取适当步骤纠正冈野进错误","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"906f845e2f"},{"id":"cababa74db","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"906f845e2f"},{"id":"1dfa0e70a5","type":"paragraph","text":"一月十四日下午四时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"906f845e2f"}],"page":{"id":"199c07ac25","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"906f845e2f","start":170,"end":170}}}},"__N_SSG":true}